    "description": "Future Innovation Group, Inc. engages in the IoT and machines businesses in Japan. The company development, sales, rental, and leasing of mobile management systems, as well as associated communication and application services and maintenance, etc.; development, operation, and maintenance of multimedia systems for hotel operators, semiconductor substrate business, and manufacturing equipment business; and research, development, manufacturing, construction, maintenance management, sales, and import/export of unmanned aircraft and robot control systems. It also engages in the development and sales of in-house call recording systems and system contract development; development of logistics systems and virtual reality systems related solutions; development of payments, robotics, and information technology; maintenance and management of information and communications systems; tourist taxi/bus business and flat-rate taxi business; and rental/lease of Mobile Create products. In addition, the company is involved in the manufacturing and sales of Mobile Create products; provision of location information services in the transportation and logistics industries; and sales of hotel multimedia systems and procurement of materials. Further, it engages in the manufacture and sale of semiconductor and automobile related manufacturing equipment, dies, transport robots, etc. The company was founded in 2002 and is based in Oita, Japan."
